==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superadvenient
<hw>Su`per*ad*ven"ient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Coming
upon; coming in addition to, or in assistance of, something.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He has done bravely by the <qex>superadvenient</qex> assistance of
his God.</q> <rj><qau>Dr. H. More.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superalimentation</ent>⟦br⟧
